01:10:15.753 --> 01:10:18.297
[Al thinking] <i>You are out of your mind.</i>

01:10:20.507 --> 01:10:24.595
<i>♪ When the day turns to night ♪</i>

01:10:25.554 --> 01:10:28.724
<i>♪ And the sun is out of sight ♪</i>

01:10:29.767 --> 01:10:30.643
