01:16:03.183 --> 01:16:06.937
<i>"Dear Al, I suck at goodbyes.</i>

01:16:09.314 --> 01:16:12.651
<i>That was the best night I've had in years.</i>

01:16:13.151 --> 01:16:14.319
<i>You're amazing,</i>

01:16:14.403 --> 01:16:17.990
<i>but you and Buddy can use
some space right now.</i>

01:16:19.449 --> 01:16:23.537
<i>Remember to take your shoes
